Text: FW Sales to Midland Cogen Cc both sitara deals have been changed to a zero volume apr out chance Original Message From Couch Greg Sent Tuesday May AM To Rabon Chance Subject FW Sales to Midland Cogen Can you handle this I do not have Sitara access Thanks Greg Original Message From Germany Chris Sent Monday May PM To Couch Greg Ryder Patrick Cc Polsky Phil Dhont Margaret Hamic Priscilla Doner Max Subject Sales to Midland Cogen We stopped serving Midland Cogen on Sitara deals and effective There are trigger prices on both of these deals which automatically generates an invoice whether we physically serve the deal or not see invoice number SA for April production For April these deals are generating a credit invoice in the amount of I would like to take the trigger volumes to effective for the term of the deal to see if this reverses out the credit created in April and keeps us from sending out a credit invoice in the future Let me know if this is an issue Thanks
